Localhost Live chat app

Please Run server.py ,first. 
    Enter your mysql root account username and password.
    Then enter openweather appid (optional)
    Your host laptop ip will appear.

Then run main.py. 
    There will be a blank screen until you enter the host ip.
    Enter host laptop ip.

*REQUIREMENT* 
-MySQL 

Modules name 

Cryptodome - "pip install pycryptodomex"
PIL - "pip instal pillow"

